HEADWORD: Stumper
<hw>Stump"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
stumps.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A boastful person.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>A puzzling or incredible story.</def> <mark>[Slang,
U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Stumpiness</ent>⟦br⟧
